<A>__{they suit up, connor and murphy in their usual masks and gloves, dad is already in his usual dark hat and glasses. the boys start for the courtroom door but dad gently holds them back. he takes a moment, then slowly removes his hat and glasses. his sons look at one another and then remove their masks. the three look into each others eyes for a moment.}
